  "detailed_description": "Cryptr is a dungeon crawler, hack and slash adventure style game with RPG elements. Cryptr aims to be a fun game featuring the works of many artists. Currently, Cryptr is single-player with multiple playable classes: <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mage (spellcasting)<br></li><li> Warrior (sword and shield)<br></li><li> Necromancer (spellcasting)<br></li><li> Archer (bow)<br></li><li> Ravager (dual melee weapons)</li></ul>  <br><br>Early Access has released on August 31, 2022. Pricing will remain the same per copy during and after Early Access.",
  "about_the_game": "Cryptr is a dungeon crawler, hack and slash adventure style game with RPG elements. Cryptr aims to be a fun game featuring the works of many artists. Currently, Cryptr is single-player with multiple playable classes: <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Mage (spellcasting)<br></li><li> Warrior (sword and shield)<br></li><li> Necromancer (spellcasting)<br></li><li> Archer (bow)<br></li><li> Ravager (dual melee weapons)</li></ul>  <br><br>Early Access has released on August 31, 2022. Pricing will remain the same per copy during and after Early Access.",
